<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-progressbar.xml">ProgressBar</db:link> indicates the progress of an operation. The value should be updated regularly. The range is defined by <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-progressbar.xml#from-prop">from</db:link> and <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls2-progressbar.xml#to-prop">to</db:link>, which both can contain any value.</db:para>
<db:informaltable style="generic">
<db:tr valign="top">
<db:td>
